io.spine.validate

Class ComparableNumber

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Number
      • io.spine.validate.ComparableNumber
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<java.lang.Number>

    @Immutable
public final class ComparableNumber
extends java.lang.Number
implements java.lang.Comparable<java.lang.Number>
    A number that can be compared to another number.

    Note that for values that are outside Long range, or when a precision beyond that of Double is required, instances of this class yield incorrect comparison results.
